cs.NI, cs.MA, cs.CR, cs.MM, cs.OS

This paper deals with the issue of seamless flow migration on mobile devices, which is primarily related to networking (cs.NI). The paper also proposes two novel system mechanisms for mobile devices, which involves machine learning (cs.MA) and security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper reports an iPhone 3GS based implementation of these mechanisms, which involves operating systems (cs.OS). Finally, the paper characterizes IP traffic on smartphones, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
